info.name: Milk Cake
info.description: Indulge in the creamy decadence of Milk Cake—a soft and delicious confection with the rich flavor of milk, caramelized to perfection on the outside, offering a delightful treat for your taste buds.

info.name: Banana Chips [200gms]
info.description: Irresistibly crunchy banana chips, born from the sun-soaked embrace of bananas, expertly sliced and lightly fried to create a symphony of tropical flavors that beckon with each blissful bite.

info.name: Chakoli (200gms)
info.description: Chakoli is a soulful South Indian delicacy, capturing the essence of celebration in its mesmerizing spiral form. Handcrafted from a blend of Besan, and a symphony of spices, these golden-brown spirals evoke a sense of nostalgia and joy.

info.name: Jawa Nimki [250gms]
info.description: Jawa Nimki, also known as Jeera Nimki, is a popular and crispy Bengali snack. These diamond-shaped treats are made from a dough of maida (refined flour), water, and cumin seeds.

info.name: Sandwich Bhakarwadi (200gms)
info.description: Sandwich Bhakarwadi is a spiced and layered Indian snack, where two dough layers sandwich a flavorful coconut filling. Deep-fried to golden perfection, it offers a delightful blend of textures and tastes in each bite.

info.name: Chana Matar Mixture (200gm)
info.description: Chana Matar Mixture is a savory blend of roasted chana, matar and an assortment of spices. This flavorful mixture provides a satisfying crunch and a burst of aromatic spices, creating a delightful snacking experience that perfectly balances texture and taste.

info.name: Aata Suhali
info.description: A savory delight expertly crafted with wheat flour and aromatic carom seeds, offering a delightful blend of flavors and a satisfying crunch in every bite.

info.name: Agra Sev (200 Gms)
info.description: A versatile delight, perfect for enhancing chaats and Raj Kachori, this flavorful snack adds a zing of taste to your favorite dishes, making them even more irresistible.

info.name: Aloo Chips [200gms]
info.description: A crispy finger snacks recipe made with thinly sliced potatoes. Potato chips are crispy and tasty aloo chips with a pleasing taste, flavored with some salt and black pepper powder.

info.name: Aloo Lacha (200 Gms)
info.description: Aloo Lachha Crunchy spiced potato sticks flavoured with a blast of red chilli, pepper and freshly ground jeera. The perfect addition to your teatime meals.

info.name: Bhakarwadi (200 Gms)
info.description: Delight in the crispy spiral magic of our Bhakarwadi – भाकरवड़ी, where layers of Besan and spicy stuffing are expertly rolled, fried to golden perfection, creating a crunchy sensation that beckons your taste buds to a symphony of handcrafted flavors.

info.name: Bhavnagari Bhujiya (250 Gms)
info.description: Experience the irresistible crunch and fiery flavor explosion of our Bhavnagari Bhujia, expertly crafted from Besan, spices, and love, meticulously fried to golden perfection for a spicy delight that dances on your palate.

info.name: Bhel Bhujiya (200 Gms)
info.description: Zesty and addictive bhel bhujiya, a tantalizing crunchy sev, meticulously crafted to deliver an explosion of flavors with every mouthwatering bite.

info.name: Bikaneri Bhujiya (200 Gm)
info.description: An irresistibly spicy and crispy delight meticulously handcrafted from Besanr, infused with aromatic spices, and deep-fried to golden perfection, promising a flavorful symphony that transports your taste buds to the vibrant streets of Bikaner.

info.name: Bikaneri Bhujiya (400 Gm)
info.description: An irresistibly spicy and crispy delight meticulously handcrafted from Besanr, infused with aromatic spices, and deep-fried to golden perfection, promising a flavorful symphony that transports your taste buds to the vibrant streets of Bikaner.

info.name: Bina Mirch Bhujia (250 Gm)
info.description: Bina mirch bhujiya, a delectable masterpiece of savory delight, skillfully crafted without chili yet bursting with flavor, combining expertly seasoned besan with a perfect crunch, inviting you to savor the spice-free magic in every crispy bite.

info.name: Chana Chips (200 Gms)
info.description: Savor the crunch of chana chips, where roasted chickpeas meet a symphony of spices, creating a wholesome snack that's meticulously crafted, crispy, and irresistibly addictive.

info.name: Chatpata Mixture (200 Gms)
info.description: Chatpata Mixture is an enticing blend of spicy treats and savory namkeen, featuring an array of crunchy elements enveloped in a harmonious combination of sweet, sour and spicy flavors.

info.name: Chota Papdi (250 Gms)
info.description: Chota Papdi, the diminutive delight, is a tiny, crispy Indian snack. Crafted from a blend of Besan, spices, and herbs, these snacks are fried to perfection, offering a delightful combination of crunch and flavorful spices.

info.name: Coated Peanuts(200 Gm)
info.description: A favorite among snack enthusiasts, coated peanuts are a crunchy and savory delight. Each peanut is skillfully coated with a delicious blend of spices, offering a flavorful and satisfying treat that's perfect for any snack craving.

info.name: Cornflakes Mixture (200 Gms)
info.description: Cornflakes mixture is a savory and crispy snack that combines the light and crunchy texture of cornflakes with a flavorful mix of spices and peanuts. This popular mixture offers a delightful balance of sweet, salty, and spicy notes, making it a perfect crunchy companion for tea or an enjoyable snack during festive occasions.

info.name: Delhi Aloo Lachcha (200 Gms)
info.description: Delhi Aloo Lacha, an enticing fusion of thinly sliced, golden-fried potatoes interwoven with spices, creating a crispy and flavorful delight that captures the essence of Delhi's street food magic in every delectable bite.

info.name: Diet Chidwa(200 Gms)
info.description: Dry Fruit Lacha is a delightful snack featuring a base of aloo lachcha (potato shreds) complemented by the richness of almonds, cashews, and raisins. Infused with a sweet flavor profile, this combination offers a unique and delicious treat.

info.name: Gujarati Mixture (250 Gms)
info.description: Gujarati Mixture refers to a popular snack originating from the Indian state of Gujarat. It typically consists of a blend of various deep-fried or roasted components such as sev, peanuts, fried chana dal and other savory elements.

info.name: Gujrati Chidwa (200 Gms)
info.description: A traditional Gujarati chidwa, crafted from dry poha, potato chips, and peanuts, offers a delightful mix of textures and flavors. This crunchy snack serves as a lovely accompaniment to a hot cup of tea, creating a perfect blend of savory and satisfying indulgence.

info.name: Jhaal Mixture (250 Gms)
info.description: Jhaal Mixture is a zesty and flavorful snack originating from Bengal, India. It is a spicy and crunchy blend of various deep-fried or roasted components, including sev, peanuts, fried lentils, and other savory elements.

info.name: Lambi Papdi / Fafra(250 Gms)
info.description: Lamba papdi, a tantalizing snack of crispy, elongated strands of Besan dough, deep-fried to a golden hue, offering a delightful crunch with each savory bite, evoking a nostalgic craving for its irresistible texture and flavor.

info.name: Masala Aloo Chips (200gms)
info.description: Indulge in the irresistible allure of masala aloo chips, thinly sliced potatoes lovingly seasoned with a symphony of spices, then crisped to perfection, inviting you to savor the tantalizing blend of flavors in every savory crunch.

info.name: Masala Aloo Lachcha[200gms]
info.description: Experience the addictive crunch of masala aloo lacha, where slender potato strands are meticulously seasoned with fragrant spices, then fried to crispy perfection, delivering a symphony of bold flavors that ignite your taste buds with every mouthwatering nibble.

info.name: Masala Boondiya (200 Gms)
info.description: Masala Boondiya is a flavorful snack created by mixing boondi, which are small, deep-fried Besan pearls, with a special blend of spices. The spices add a delightful and savory kick to the boondi, enhancing its taste. It often served with chutney or Dahi.

info.name: Masala Khankhra(250gms)
info.description: Experience the spicy sensation of masala khankra, where thin, crispy wheat discs are seasoned with a blend of tantalizing spices and roasted to perfection, promising a flavorful explosion in every crunchy bite.

info.name: Masala Mathi [2 Pieces]
info.description: Masala Mathi is a spiced and savory Indian snack made from , which are flaky and crisp wheat crackers. These crackers are stuffed with aromatic spices such as cumin, coriander, ajwain.

info.name: Masala Suhaali (200gms)
info.description: Masala Suhali is a spiced and flaky Indian snack made from a seasoned dough of all-purpose flour, and spices. Deep-fried until golden, it offers a delightful blend of layers, textures, and savory flavors, perfect for festive occasions or tea-time indulgence.

info.name: Mathi (5 Pcs)
info.description: 500gms

info.name: Mini Samosa (200 Gms)
info.description: Mini Samosas are bite-sized delights, featuring golden triangles with a spicy and flavorful filling. These mini versions of India's favorite snack boast flaky crusts and extra delicious centers, offering a perfect blend of crunch and taste in every bite.

info.name: Moong Chips (200gms)
info.description: Moong Chips are savory snacks made from moong dal (split green gram). These chips are seasoned with a delightful blend of spices, offering a perfect balance of spiciness, sweetness, and tanginess.

info.name: Mota Bhujiya (250 Gm)
info.description: Mota Bhujiya is a popular Indian snack known for its robust flavor and satisfying crunch. This snack typically consists of thick and crunchy sev (fried Besan vermicelli) seasoned with a blend of spices.

info.name: Mota Bhujiya (50 Gm)
info.description: Mota Bhujiya is a popular Indian snack known for its robust flavor and satisfying crunch. This snack typically consists of thick and crunchy sev (fried Besan vermicelli) seasoned with a blend of spices.

info.name: Mota Bhujiya (500 Gm)
info.description: Mota Bhujiya is a popular Indian snack known for its robust flavor and satisfying crunch. This snack typically consists of thick and crunchy sev (fried Besan vermicelli) seasoned with a blend of spices.

info.name: Murrukku (200 Gms)
info.description: Murukku is a South Indian snack, crispy delights made from a blend of rice flour and spices. Deep-fried to perfection, it's a popular choice during festive occasions.

info.name: Phool Gathiya (250 Gms)
info.description: Phool Gathiya is a popular Indian snack known for its unique twisted, flower-like shape. This crispy and savory treat is made from Besan (besan) mixed with spices such as ajwain, turmeric.

info.name: Raita Bundiya (200 Gms)
info.description: Raita boondiya is a crispy Besan ball which is used for making boondiya to add an extra crunch to your meal.

info.name: Soya Sticks (200 Gms)
info.description: Soya Sticks are crunchy and wholesome snacks made from soy flour. These tasty crisps are often enjoyed during tea or coffee breaks, offering a flavorful and satisfying treat with each bite.

info.name: Suhali [250gms]
info.description: Suhali is a flaky and crispy Indian pastry made from flour, deep-fried to golden perfection. It's a popular treat during festivals and tea-time.

info.name: Suhali (500 Gm)
info.description: Suhali is a flaky and crispy Indian pastry made from flour, deep-fried to golden perfection. It's a popular treat during festivals and tea-time.

info.name: Kashmiri Dalmoth (250 Gms)
info.description: Kashmiri Dalmooth is a traditional and savory snack. This flavorful mixture combines yellow lentils, almonds and spices to create a crunchy and satisfying treat.

info.name: Butterscotch Sandesh (1pc)
info.description: Butterscotch Sandesh is a Bengali sweet, blending the classic Sandesh with the rich and buttery flavor of butterscotch. This fusion treat offers a unique and delightful combination of traditional sweetness and indulgent taste.

info.name: Chamcham [1pc]
info.description: Cham Cham is a beloved Bengali sweet, crafted from paneer, khoya, soaked in sugar syrup, and often flavored with cardamom. It boasts a soft, melt-in-the-mouth texture, perfect for celebrations.

info.name: Choco Ball (1pc)
info.description: Savor the heavenly decadence of choco ball sandesh, where creamy Paneer is blended with rich cocoa, molded into irresistible spheres, and garnished with a sprinkle of chocolate, inviting you to indulge in a divine fusion of flavors with every blissful bite.

info.name: Chocolate Bite (1pc)
info.description: Chocolate Bite Sandesh is a fusion Bengali sweet, blending the classic Sandesh with the indulgent taste of chocolate. These bite-sized treats offer a delightful harmony of traditional sweetness and chocolaty richness.

info.name: Gulab Patti Sandesh (1pc)
info.description: Gulab Patti Sandesh is a unique Bengali sweet, infusing the classic Sandesh with the aromatic essence of rose.topped with rose petals. Perfect for special occasions.

info.name: Kesar Sandesh (1pc)
info.description: Kesar Sandesh is a vibrant Bengali sweet, blending the classic Sandesh with the essence of saffron. It offers a perfect harmony of traditional texture and exotic saffron aroma, often garnished with khoya.

info.name: Malai Cham Cham (1pc)
info.description: Satisfy your sweet cravings with malai cham cham, where soft, pillowy cylendrical shaped chenna are simmered in creamy milk, infused with cardamom, offering a heavenly delight that melts in your mouth with each indulgent bite.

info.name: Mango Roll [1pc]
info.description: Mango Roll Sandesh is a luscious Bengali sweet, uniting the classic Sandesh with the irresistible taste of ripe mangoes. A delightful fusion for indulging in the mango season.

info.name: Strawberry Roll [1pc]
info.description: Strawberry Roll Sandesh is a fruity Bengali sweet, blending the classic Sandesh with the sweet and tangy flavor of strawberries.

info.name: Kaju Barfi
info.description: Kaju Barfi is a classic Indian diamond shaped sweet made from cashews. With a rich and creamy texture, garnished with edible silver leaf.

info.name: Kaju Barfi [1 Piece]
info.description: Kaju Barfi is a classic Indian diamond shaped sweet made from cashews. With a rich and creamy texture, garnished with edible silver leaf.
